{"tid":1220023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[食住個勢] 台灣6月23日於台北舉行無分派別的反親中媒體遊行","createTime":"2019-06-14T02:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T12:44:02.000Z","uid":33905,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4e9cd123350432e68d25c531c6da1e9a22eab92b","tid":1220023,"uid":33905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:20:51.000Z","msg":"見連登無人POST, 希望PO黎引起反中態勢已經史無前例既連登仔們注意同支持<br />\n<br />\n事源正直香港宜家反送中條例既激烈示威, 好大程度上已經引起左台仔們既注意, 直接導致現任總統蔡英文係民進黨2020總統大選的初選勝出,詳情可以睇以下呢個POST<br />\n<br />\n林奠打亂中共統一台灣如意算盤 下場會係點?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1215347/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1215347/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n香港傳左個單刀波比蔡英文<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1215347/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1215347/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n但係件事不斷發酵之前, 台灣既親中紅色媒體已經不斷好似CCTVB咁抹黑係金鐘努力緊既抗爭者(呢方面我唔熟台灣電視台,真係俾唔出醬油, 希望有巴打接力)<br />\n<br />\n而知道事實既台灣仔們, 其實在此之前已經因為親中媒體為左製造[韓]流, 不斷放送韓國瑜既新聞深感不滿, 甚至其中最紅既中天新聞已經俾人罰過錢:<br />\n<br />\n播放太多韓國瑜新聞 台灣中天電視被罰百萬新台幣<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/272525/%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E3%80%80%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A9%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E8%A2%AB%E7%BD%B0%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E6%96%B0%E5%8F%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F272525%2F%25E6%2592%25AD%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25A4%259A%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2591%259C%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258F%25B0%2F&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=d4c6d6d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/272525/%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E3%80%80%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A9%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E8%A2%AB%E7%BD%B0%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E6%96%B0%E5%8F%B0/</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n終於係前日, 台灣實況界KOL館長忍唔撚住, 係實況入面怒屌親中媒體並提議發起遊行, 意見亦都馬上被時代力量立委黃國昌接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n館長本人:<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/x5pw6A2qDSoicxKqZpJRJg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/cts.com.tw/84b59f65beee2cead1a10617afa4e0d3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fx5pw6A2qDSoicxKqZpJRJg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fcts.com.tw%2F84b59f65beee2cead1a10617afa4e0d3&h=f3298b13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係YAHOO既新聞提要:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不爽韓稱中華民國「地區」館長號召6/23上街反中媒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%8D%E7%88%BD%E9%9F%93%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E9%A4%A8%E9%95%B7%E8%99%9F%E5%8F%AC-623-%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E5%8F%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%AA%92-015531175.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%2588%25BD%25E9%259F%2593%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2599%259F%25E5%258F%25AC-623-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AA%2592-015531175.html&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=f066901f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%8D%E7%88%BD%E9%9F%93%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E9%A4%A8%E9%95%B7%E8%99%9F%E5%8F%AC-623-%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E5%8F%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%AA%92-015531175.html</a><br />\n<br />\n香港反送中示威爆發流血衝突引發全球關注，國內政治人物也紛表態不接受「一國兩制」，但高雄市長韓國瑜自稱中華民國「地區」的發言不但遭外界抨擊自我矮化，更惹火網紅館長陳之漢怒嗆「這就是你們要選的總統嗎」？宣布將參加6月23日（周日）由時代力量立委黃國昌在凱道舉辦的「反中媒」活動，要親中的紅色媒體滾出台灣！<br />\n<br />\n不爽高雄市長韓國瑜稱中華民國「地區」，館長直播怒嗆「這就是你們要選的總統嗎」？號召大家參加6月23日（周日）由時代力量立委黃國昌在凱道舉辦的「反中媒」活動，請親中的紅色媒體滾出台灣！（圖片翻攝Youtube/寶寶愛館長）<br />\n不爽高雄市長韓國瑜稱中華民國「地區」，館長直播怒嗆「這就是你們要選的總統嗎」？號召大家參加6月23日（周日）由時代力量立委黃國昌在凱道舉辦的「反中媒」活動，請親中的紅色媒體滾出台灣！（圖片翻攝Youtube/寶寶愛館長）<br />\n更多<br />\n館長昨在直播中對香港反送中示威表示「香港是東方之珠哎，民眾被打成這樣，你（指韓國瑜）沒有撻伐、沒有罵，這就是你們崇拜的韓神」？並指出黃國昌6月23日將在凱道舉辦「反中媒」活動，他會到場參加，要親中媒體滾出台灣！<br />\n<br />\n館長要求NCC應要管控這些中媒，「這些媒體每天報導高雄市長韓國瑜的新聞占60%，國際上和香港的新聞都報反方向的，全部的新聞都偏向中國，台灣的政府到底要不要管？立委要不要立法去管控這些『收了中國解放軍的錢，來台灣要用媒體統人民的思想，你政府為何不管？你看我們老人家被洗腦多嚴重」！<br />\n<br />\n「現場沒有錢、沒有便當，就是一份愛國心！」館長強調或許人不多，但他絕對會去，「至少我無愧祖先，我盡力了」；黃國昌也在臉書透露已借到6月23日凱道路權，呼籲大家一起站出來，「拒絕紅色媒體、守護台灣民主」！<br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴打睇完都係呢個POST留一留言支持台仔, 佢地都有一大部分人MON住連登, 唇亡齒寒, 敵人既敵人就係我地隊友, 台灣人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋大家要明白宜家呢個時勢, 已經證明左我地無論69既百萬人和平遊行, 定係612出黎抗爭既巴打們全部都係有用既, 除左反送中本身會有更加的noise之外, 亦都會令到全球開始漫延一股反中既浪潮!<br />\n<br />\n大家記住, <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各種文宣我地千其唔好停, 今個星期日616亦都一定要繼續企出黎遊行!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"22e8a256bebcabbaaacc4a40e789207ae4e4ec62","tid":1220023,"uid":33905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5581e60ed1da0eff150578a68108f32af87cead2","tid":1220023,"uid":33905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:22:38.000Z","msg":"支持台仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a16a11359485db0ae05699abcd40af4868766a8","tid":1220023,"uid":33905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:23:02.000Z","msg":"推POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e67815f4cc9b3ae2bcb2b4aa0c807a459894019","tid":1220023,"uid":33905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0c0fcda83f3965a94bcb3c70af2c88dfc03a82","tid":1220023,"uid":33905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165a399d7316f25669a6fd49a39e939f5d4d4ef3","tid":1220023,"uid":33905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0695d1e1833007cb9c99bbf46c03684c3b3edf","tid":1220023,"uid":33905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b184872e946ace4dcdf568d4b1cf15567d68c19c","tid":1220023,"uid":5809,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:25:17.000Z","msg":"台仔好波，係你地大選結果出之前都唔再鬧你地台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁多位香港人,大家認為星期日上街係為左咩!?<br />\n<br />\n為左抗惡法?無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗迫林鄭下台?無錯</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但最重要既係保護香港人!!!!!!!!!!</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時最少已經有11個香港人為咗我地被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當中包括為咗我地而食棍!!!中椒!!!同埋中槍既香港人!!!!!!<br />\n星期日上街我地一定要為佢地發聲!!!唔可以忘記佢地!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n大家集中目標:<br />\n1.撤回送中惡法<br />\n2.林鄭及相關官員必須問責下台<br />\n3.釋放所有被捕人士及保證不會檢控任何示威者<br /